full_text:
If anyone feels like calibrating their board, or wants to know if they can get accurate information from it, I have written down a number between 1 and a billion (1,000,000,000)

Let me know what your board thinks it is. 
If it gets it correct, sounds like you&#39;ve got something important going on there!

If it can&#39;t get it correct, I suppose that brings into suspect all its other answers.





